phrases: Report on the Investigation of Tsutsugami Gai
Shu will hold them back with Inori's Void.
During that time, we will seize the second truck.
The target will be at the attack point in six,
Commander to all units, abort mission!
I beg you, please tell me
Promise you will make your big sister happy.
Summer's sun clouded over, the wind streamed by
It is a sandwich, is that okay?
You know, you surprised me yesterday
when you messaged me out of nowhere asking for help.
You are not going to tell me anything?
Why do not you want to go home?
Well, you can tell me when you feel like it.
You are not going to answer?
No, let him be for now.
It is been a while, has not it,
That is what my comrades call me.
I certainly never thought you were his son.
Which means I have to ask you...
Tsutsugami Gai, why do you fight?
There is one special woman out there that I want to hold in my arms.
That is why I am fighting.
Saving Japan is a side project to getting your woman, eh?
The rock we discussed will be brought to Haneda the day after tomorrow.
It seems Yan is trying to transport it overseas.
It is something that should remain in the grasp of the Japanese.
We will use all our strength to stop them.
Who would have thought this rock, the object of every nation's desire,
would fall into my hands like this...
This will take you another step closer to the White House.
You are an ambitious woman, Emily.
I suppose the unknown is Keido.
He steals this, and then instead of running he waltzes right back here?
I am so glad you feel like coming back to school, Shu!
I mean, it is really not good for you to hole up in that place forever.
I will go get you some water.
What is the matter with you?
Do not tell me you are ready to give up on everything
just because you could not save one kid with the cancer?
I thought I could do it.
So I thought I could be like Gai.
I cannot believe you are wallowing in self-pity!
Give me just a little more
We know where the stolen rock that started it all is.
We are running a recovery mission.
It is got nothing to do with me!
I never wanted this stupid power in the first place!
I am sick of it, do you hear me?
They say it is possible to isolate the Void Genome if its possessor dies.
You are a dead man now.
Do not show your face in front of us again.
I will have Inori pull out, too.
I was stupid to think for even a second that you were one of us!
YOU-Um, calls or texts or something... can we...
I would like you to listen to it, Shu.
I think I must have wanted to be like Gai.
So it is better this way.
It should be better this way, but...
Yan will be temporarily returning home on that craft with some top-secret materials.
Our duty is to see him safely off!
The Major General should be arriving any minute now.
Did you fall in love with him?
Tell me, Gai, do I love Shu?
So you chose him too, in the end.
We will think about this afterward.
What do you mean by this, Chief Keido?
How could you use Kurosu's ID to steal that rock,
not to mention hand it over to Major General Yan?!
I saw a familiar face on the island.
He is grown a lot, has not he?
Do not involve Shu in this!
It is too late for that.
He is already inherited the King's Power.
He is in with the Undertakers, too.
You have met her too, have not you?
Do you really believe a girl with that face, that body,
is by his side through mere coincidence?
We will be at Point B in 30.
After that point there are surveillance cameras and monitors
that I cannot control from here, so be careful.
We have thirty minutes until our objective's transport plane takes off.
My team will seize the plane before then.
The Endlave unit will deploy when we announce the seizure and back us up.
You summoned me out here too, so do not screw it up.
We have been expecting you, Major General Yan!
Switch the camera to channel G7.
There is no such channel, Sir...
After all, I just now set it up.
It will be outputted from every channel in the city that is under GHQ control.
All my beloved members of the Anti Bodies,
I repeat: All my beloved members of the Anti Bodies,
I trust this will do, Chief Keido?
Do not come crying to me later.
But... it is too late to back out now.
I am sending you to heaven!
I wish I would gotten to hear the rest of the lecture.
I like the Classics a lot, you know.
Come on, I say so all the time!
Let me be close to you, Hare.
After all... you love me, do not you?
Try telling me exactly what you did wrong!
You are not seeing me at all, Shu.
Do not make me a substitute for Yuzuriha!
Did your big new power make it so you cannot even see yourself anymore?
I saw you draw something like scissors out of Yahiro and destroy an Endlave.
I felt so bad for you then...
And I wanted to help cheer you up somehow...
But that Shu just now was not okay!
That is not the Shu I love!
Crap, the controls do not work!
Do not tell me he is activated the stone?!
I have come to fetch you...
What can you possibly be thinking of?!
Let us finish what we started on that day... on that Christmas we lost!
This is not the right song!
Really, Shuichiro, you are old enough to know better.
You are as entertaining as always.
and tries to hurt you with cruel words,
even if the world does not try to believe you
and places a crown of thorns upon your head,
I can take your side, and yours alone
I know your pain and loneliness
So everything that makes me whole
I will give that to you now
These days you love me no more
nor am I still treasured by you
What did you tell me when we parted?
The words hung in midair and never reached me
I know my dreams and wishes are illusory
and yet I cannot give up on them
You said, Do not let go, hold onto my hand
and, We will always be together
Your hands as I held them were warm
